head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths WARNE, FREDERICK P.

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths WARNE, FREDERICK P.

block.p: WARNE-Frederick P. Ret. General Counsel for Ethyl Corp. In North Banford, CT, of Evergreen Woods, 88 Notch Hill Rd. Husband of Susanne Sanders Warne of North Branford. Father of David S. Warne, Elizabeth W. Nowak and Susan W. Warne. Brother of Helena Lieb. Also survived by four grandchildren. Services private. For information, Guilford Funeral Home, 115 Church St, Guilford, CT.
